BioYeast

The undirected graph BioYeast has 1458 nodes and 1948 edges.

RAM requirements

The RAM requirements for the nodes and edges data structures are 178.82KB and 5.87KB respectively.

Degree centrality

The minimum node degree is 1, the maximum node degree is 56, the mode degree is 1, the mean degree is 2.67 and the node degree median is 2.

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 157 (degree 56), 26 (degree 38), 55 (degree 30), 69 (degree 29) and 58 (degree 29).
